20Zers%2C%20aged%2018-26%2C%20fearing%20they%20are%20not%20on%20track.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Smiling%20young%20man%20looks%20at%20his%20cell%20phone%20with%20a%20colorful%20city%20street%20behind%20him%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b6b2911ccd1e00198aa166%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMost%20Gen%20Zers%20and%20millennials%20feel%20they%20are%20on%20track%20financially%20for%20retirement.%3Cp%3EHinterhaus%20Productions%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20pressures%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bfinancial%20vortex%26quot%3B%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lack%20of%20confidence%20in%20meeting%20retirement%20goals%20is%20due%20in%20large%20part%20to%20what%20Goldman%20Sachs%20calls%20the%20%26quot%3Bfinancial%20vortex%26quot%3B%20of%20competing%20priorities%2C%20as%20well%20as%20taking%20the%20time%20to%20have%20a%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldman%20Sachs%20notes%20that%20people%20struggle%20to%20balance%20multiple%20financial%20goals%20with%20limited%20financial%20resources.%20Money%20that%20would%20go%20to%20retirement%20savings%20is%20also%20being%20tugged%20into%20the%20financial%20vortex%20by%20things%20like%20credit%20card%20debt%2C%20student%20loans%2C%20college%2C%20care%20for%20children%20and%20older%20adults%2C%20and%20financial%20hardships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20their%20survey%20of%205%2C261%20US%20participants%20in%20June%20and%20July%2C%20using%20a%20financial%20plan%20has%20a%20significant%20impact%20on%20how%20confident%20people%20are%20that%20they%20will%20meet%20their%20retirement%20needs%20on%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20those%20with%20a%20plan%2C%2079%25%20of%20respondents%20are%20on%20track%20or%20ahead%20of%20schedule%20for%20retirement.%20Meanwhile%2C%20only%2034%25%20of%20people%20without%20a%20plan%20had%20the%20same%20confidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnly%2060%25%20of%20those%20surveyed%20ha