till%20fresh%20in%20the%20minds%20of%20people.%20The%20Kaala%20Paani%20storyline%20looks%20beyond%20disease%20and%20devastation%20and%20blends%20fiction%20and%20truth%20to%20delve%20into%20the%20reasons%20behind%20the%20public%20health%20crisis%20-%20deforestation%2C%20threats%20posed%20to%20an%20endangered%20indigenous%20community%2C%20industry-government%20nexus%20and%20corruption%20at%20various%20levels%20of%20the%20local%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20sense%20of%20dread%20and%20gloom%20pervades%20the%20islands%20as%20Leptospiral%20Hemorrhagic%20Fever%20(LHF-27)%20turns%20rampant.%20Citizens%20and%20medical%20professionals%20are%20up%20against%20an%20enemy%20that%20is%20invisible%2C%20Nature%2C%20which%20has%20borne%20the%20brunt%20of%20mankind's%20greed%20for%20centuries%20and%20is%20now%20striking%20back.%20The%20seven-episode%20series%20derives%20strength%20from%20the%20ethical%2C%20psychological%20and%20environmental%20questions%20that%20it%20raises.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20Panchatantra%20story%20about%20a%20frog%20and%20a%20scorpion%20is%20used%20to%20underline%20the%20nature%20of%20goodness%20and%20dishonesty%20in%20present%20times.%20The%20%26quot%3Btrolley%20problem%26quot%3B%20thought%20experiment%20alludes%20to%20the%20situation%20on%20the%20ground%20-%20the%20administration%20is%20in%20a%20make-or-break%20moral%20quandary.%20Is%20it%20fine%20to%20sacrifice%20one%20person%20in%20order%20to%20save%20thousands%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EKaala%20Paani%3C%2Fem%3E%20situates%20numerous%20significant%20stories%2C%20contemporary%20and%20historical%2C%20in%20the%20collective%20and%20the%20personal%20in%20search%20of%20an%20answer%20to%20that%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%C2%A0%3Cem%3EKaala%20Paani%3C%2Fem%3E%20cast%20is%20led%20by%20Mona%20Singh%20and%20Ashutosh%20Gowariker%20but%20it%20is%20Sukant%20Goel%2C%20playing%20a%20Port%20Blair%20taxi%20operator%2C%20who%20hogs%20the%20lion's%20share%20of%20the%20spotlight.%20The%20gifted%20actor%20does%20full%20justice%20to%20a%20strong%20author-backed%20role%20that%20allows%20him%20to%20mine%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20emotions%2C%20from%20the%20frothy%20and%20flippant%20to%20the%20intense%20and%20unsettling.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlso%20impressive%20are%20the%20key%20supporting%20actors%2C%20each%20playing%20a%20character%20with%20a%20past%20marred%20by%20trauma%20and%20unpleasant%20experiences%20that%20take%20some%20doing%20to%20live%20down.%20From%20violence%20to%20toxic%20masculinity%20and%20social%20ostracism%20to%20professional%20hurdles%2C%20these%20individuals%20have%20been%20though%20a%20lot%20and%20what%20they%20encounter%20during%20the%20epidemic%20is%20an%20opportunity%20for%20them%20to%20redeem%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVikas%20Kumar%20plays%20Santosh%20Savla%2C%20a%20tourist%20from%20Bokaro%20who%20has%20travelled%20to%20Andaman%20and%20Nicobar%20Islands%20with%20his%20wife%20and%20two%20children%20to%20attend%20a%20tourist%20festival.%20The%20man%2C%20benign%20and%20soft-hearted%2C%20banks%20upon%20his%20wife%20Gargi%20(Sarika%20Singh)%20to%20be%20the%20family's%20pillar%20of%20strength%20through%20thick%20and%20thin.%20In%20a%20severe%20crisis%20situation%2C%20Santosh%20has%20to%20dig%20deep%20into%20his%20reserves%20of%20endurance%20as%20he%20is%20buffeted%20by%20separation%2C%20loss%20and%20bereavement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EArushi%20Sharma%20is%20Jyotsna%20Dey%2C%20an%20aspiring%20nurse%20who%20has%20abandoned%20her%20ambition%20following%20a%20violent%20incident%20in%20Pune%20that%20has%20singed%20her%20for%20good.%20Her%20shot%20at%20redemption%20rests%20on%20ensuring%20the%20safety%20of%20two%20children%20separated%20from%20their%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERadhika%20Mehrotra%20plays%20medical%20intern%20Ritu%20Gagra%2C%20who%20joins%20the%20team%20of%20Dr%20Soudamini%20Singh%20(Mona%20Singh)%2C%20a%20grouchy%2C%20cynical%20but%20exceptionally%20committed%20professional%20who%20lives%20with%20a%20German%20Shepherd%20aptly%20called%20Mister%2C%20as%20the%20latter's%20hospital%20faces%20a%20severe%20staff%20shortage%20in%20the%20face%20of%20the%20health%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmey%20Wagh%20delivers%20an%20energetic%20but%20delightfully%20layered%20performance%20as%20police%20officer%20Ketan%20Kamat%2C%20a%20man%20given%20to%20fishing%20in%20troubled%20waters%20and%20saving%20his%20own%20skin%20come%20what%20may.%20And%20Chinmay%20Mandlekar%20gets%20into%20the%20skin%20of%20a%20doctor%20under%20understandable%20duress%20aggravated%20by%20a%20tragedy%20that%20hits%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20major%20tourist%20festival%20is%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20away%20and%20thousands%20of%20visitors%20have%20arrived%20in%20Port%20Blair.%20Panic%20spreads%20as%20word%20gets%20around%20that%20a%20mysterious%20killer%20disease%20has%20descended%20on%20the%20islands.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20administration%2C%20led%20by%20Admiral%20Zibran%20Qadri%20(Asuthosh%20Gowariker)%2C%20the%20central%20hospital%20under%20Dr%20Soudamini%20Singh's%20charge%2C%20individuals%20like%20Chiranjeevi%20(Sukant%20Goel)%20whose%20livelihood%20depends%20on%20the%20influx%20of%20tourists%20and%20infected%20locals%20and%20several%20outsiders%20are%20sucked%20into%20the%20maelstrom.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20crisis%20is%2C%20of%20course%2C%20not%20directly%20of%20the%20tourists'%20making.%20The%20plunder%20of%20tribal%20land%20and%20unsustainable%20development%20models%20have%20pushed%20the%20scenic%20islands%20to%20the%20brink.%20A%20multi-billion-dollar%20MNC%2C%20with%20the%20connivance%20of%20elements%20in%20the%20bureaucracy%20and%20the%20police%2C%20seeks%20to%20extend%20its%20hold%20on%20the%20land%20the%20forests%20stand%20on%20and%20the%20people%20that%20the%20forests%20belong%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20struggle%20to%20save%20lives%20coincides%20with%20the%20race%20to%20find%20the%20cause%20of%20the%20epidemic%20and%20a%20cure.%20The%20narrative%20revolves%20around%20the%20fate%20on%20endangered%20indigenous%20community%20that%20has%20lives%20in%20the%20forest%20for%2060%2C000%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EKaala%20Paani%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20well-acted%2C%20wonderfully%20crafted%20and%20consistently%20watchable%20drama%20the%20skirts%20around%20the%20pitfalls%20of%20a%20multi-pronged%20narrative.%20It%20devises%20ways%20not%20to%20let%20one%20thematic%20idea%20get%20in%20the%20way%20of%20another.%20All%20the%20strands%20come%20together%20neatly%20and%20with%20exceptional%20clarity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20cautionary%20tale%20does%20the%20tightrope%20walk%20between%20the%20depiction%20of%20an%20epidemic%20and%20its%20fallout%20and%20the%20placement%20of%20it%20in%20a%20larger%20ecological%20context%20with%20skill%20and%20balance.%20A%20series%20that%20has%20much%20to%20show%20for%20its%20efforts.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697617320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fg6ci5m78_mona-_625x300_18_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fkaala-paani-review-well-acted-wonderfully-crafted-drama-3-stars-4491990%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kaala%20Paani%20Review%3A%20The%20cautionary%20tale%20does%20the%20tightrope%20walk%20between%20the%20depiction%20of%20an%20epidemic%20and%20its%20fallout%20and%20the%20placement%20of%20it%20in%20a%20larger%20ecological%20context%20with%20skill%20and%20balance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fkaala-paani-review-well-acted-wonderfully-crafted-drama-3-stars-4491990%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pulwama%20Attack%3A%20Kin%20of%20Slain%20Jawans%20Demand%20Answers%20from%20Centre%2C%20to%20Hold%20Protest%20March%20in%20Delhi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18123003%2Ffeb0974ca9f958fb65c49849897887b5.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20family%20members%20of%2040%20CRPF%20jawans%20who%20were%20killed%20in%20the%202019%20Pulwama%20attack%20are%20planning%20to%20hold%20a%20protest%20march%20in%20Delhi%20on%20November%2026%20to%20demand%20a%20White%20Paper%20from%20the%20government%20to%20fix%20accountability%20for%20the%20alleged%20lapses%20that%20led%20to%20the%20fatal%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20banner%20of%C2%A0Confederation%20of%20Ex-Paramilitary%20Forces%20Welfare%20Associations%2C%20the%20widows%20of%20the%20slain%20jawans%20and%20their%20family%20members%20will%20voice%20their%20demands%20to%20the%20government%20in%20a%20protest%20demonstration%20to%20be%20held%20on%20November%2026%2C%20which%20is%20celebrated%20as%20Constitution%20Day%2C%20Ranbir%20Singh%2C%20the%20national%20coordinator%20of%20the%20association%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Farmy-welfare-group-to-stage-protest-against-narendra-modi-government-to-demand-answers-on-pulwama-attack%2Fcid%2F1974039%5C%22%3Etold%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20plan%20to%20bring%20widows%20and%20family%20members%20of%20the%2040%20CRPF%20jawans%20who%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20terror%20attack.%20It%20has%20been%20over%20four%20years%20since%20the%20Pulwama%20attack%20and%20the%20government%20has%20failed%20to%20fix%20accountability%20and%20responsibility%20on%20those%20officials%20whose%20failure%20led%20to%20the%20killing%20of%20our%2040%20jawans%2C%E2%80%9D%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20went%20on%20to%20add%20that%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%2C%20which%20always%20uses%20the%20nationalism%20plank%20during%20elections%2C%20has%20yet%20to%20come%20clean%20on%20what%20led%20to%20the%20killing%20of%20the%2040%20CRPF%20personnel.%20On%20February%2014%2C%202019%2C%20the%20Jawans%20were%20killed%20when%20a%20bomb%20blew%20up%20the%20bus%20they%20were%20travelling%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20families%20of%20the%2040%20slain%20CRPF%20jawans%20have%20every%20right%20to%20know%20who%20was%20responsible%20for%20the%20negligence%20of%20intelligence%20reports%20that%20proved%20fatal%20for%20our%20jawans%2C%E2%80%9D%20Singh%20affirmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20referred%20to%20explosive%20allegations%20made%20by%20former%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20governor%20Satya%20Pal%20Malik%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Db8wmHUhLvOI%26t%3D2915s%5C%22%3Einterview%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20attack%20was%20a%20result%20of%20intelligence%20failure%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20Modi%20government.%20In%20that%20interview%2C%20Malik%20said%20that%20Modi%20had%20told%20him%20%E2%80%9C%3Ci%3Etum%20abhi%20chup%20raho%3C%2Fi%3E%20(you%20keep%20quiet%20now)%E2%80%9D%20after%20he%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20refusal%20of%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20give%20an%20aircraft%20to%20ferry%20jawans%20led%20to%20their%20killing.%20Malik%20also%20went%20on%20to%20repeat%20the%20allegations%20later%20in%20different%20meetings%20that%20he%20attended.%20Subsequently%2C%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20issued%20summons%20against%20him%20in%20connection%20with%20an%20alleged%20health%20insurance%20scam%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20Malik%E2%80%99s%20allegations%2C%20Singh%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20been%20over%20four%20years%20since%20then%2C%20but%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20failed%20to%20fix%20accountability.%20Winning%20elections%20is%20his%20only%20priority.%20The%20people%20of%20this%20country%20need%20to%20remain%20alert%20that%20similar%20attacks%20can%20happen%20this%20time%20too%20before%20the%20parliamentary%20polls.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESingh%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20government%20instead%20of%20fixing%20its%20responsibility%20is%20trying%20to%20silence%20those%20who%20have%20been%20demanding%20accountability%20by%20unleashing%20probe%20agencies%20against%20them%2C%20alluding%20to%20CBI%20summons%20to%20Malik.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMalik%20had%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CModi%20had%20politicised%20the%20killings%20of%2040%20CRPF%20soldiers%20and%20the%20IAF%20strikes%20in%20Balakot%20during%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20and%20had%20even%20asked%20first-time%20voters%20to%20dedicate%20their%20vote%20to%20the%20valiant%20soldiers%20who%20carried%20out%20the%20air%20strike%20in%20Balakot.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Pulwama%20attack%20took%20eight%20weeks%20before%20the%202019%20parliament%20elections%2C%20which%20led%20to%20the%20victory%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%20with%20a%20mandate%20bigger%20than%20the%202014%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697617234000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18123003%2Ffeb0974ca9f958fb65c49849897887b5.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fpulwama-attack-kin-of-slain-jawans-demand-answers-from-centre-to-hold-protest-march-in-delhi%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20allegations%20that%20there%20were%20lapses%20on%20the%20part%20of%20intelligence%20agencies%20that%20led%20to%20the%20terror%20attack%20on%20February%2014%2C%202019%2C%20family%20members%20of%20the%20slain%20jawans%20demand%20a%20White%20Paper%20from%20the%20government.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fpulwama-attack-kin-of-slain-jawans-demand-answers-from-centre-to-hold-protest-march-in-delhi%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'I%20was%20groaning%20in%20pain'%3A%20World's%20hottest%20chilli%20revealed%20after%2010-year%20effort%20to%20break%20record%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697617200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F10%2F768x432%2Fskynews-pepper-hottest-world_6325340.jpg%3F20231018081248%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2