26%2Fpune-startup-innovates-ai-based-technology-screen-tuberculosis-within-seconds-innovation-in-healthcare%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emoved%20to%20Pune%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20his%20engineering%20course.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20when%20I%20was%20in%20Pune%20when%20things%20started%20to%20go%20downhill.%20I%20was%20in%20a%20relationship%20with%20a%20person%20and%20it%20did%20not%20work%20out.%20I%20was%20not%20doing%20good%20at%20college%20either.%20Suddenly%2C%20life%20felt%20hard%20and%20I%20felt%20alone%20in%20all%20of%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls%20adding%20that%20he%20felt%20helpless.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fraj-dagwar-1-1697611896.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Raj%20suffered%20from%20depression%20for%20about%20seven%20months%20before%20getting%20help%20from%20a%20college%20therapist.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fraj-dagwar-1-1697611896.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fraj-dagwar-1-1697611896-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fraj-dagwar-1-1697611896-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fraj-dagwar-1-1697611896-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fraj-dagwar-1-1697611896-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332491%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERaj%20suffered%20from%20depression%20for%20about%20seven%20months%20before%20getting%20help%20from%20a%20college%20therapist.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Raj%20Dagwar%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20could%20not%20see%20any%20purpose%20to%20my%20life%20and%20everything%20seemed%20bleak.%20I%20would%20lock%20myself%20in%20my%20room%20and%20not%20come%20out%20for%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20adversely%20affected%20my%20attendance%20and%20academic%20performance.%20I%20did%20not%20eat%20for%20days%20and%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20in%20a%20bottomless%20pit%20of%20darkness.%20In%20big%20cities%2C%20my%20generation%20faces%20a%20haunting%20isolation%20amidst%20the%20rush%20towards%20goals.%20When%20going%20through%20struggles%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20easy%20to%20be%20consumed%20by%20this%20loneliness%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESuffering%20silently%2C%20Raj%20could%20not%20communicate%20with%20either%20his%20friends%20or%20family%20about%20how%20he%20was%20feeling.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20start%20feeling%20depressed%2C%20it%20becomes%20very%20scary.%20It%20was%20very%20hard%20for%20me%20to%20talk%20about%20what%20I%20was%20feeling.%20When%20I%20did%20speak%20to%20my%20parents%2C%20they%20were%20not%20able%20to%20understand%20it.%20They%20would%20say%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98sir%20dard%20hai%20to%20dawai%20lele%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fem%3E(if%20you%20have%20a%20headache%2C%20take%20medicine).%20It%20was%20very%20hard%20for%20them%20to%20understand%20that%20depression%20is%20different%20from%20physical%20illnesses%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHaving%20failed%20to%20get%20support%20from%20his%20parents%2C%20Raj%20says%20he%20became%20even%20more%20closed%20off.%20%E2%80%9CI%20started%20to%20keep%20to%20myself%20and%20my%20head%20would%20keep%20buzzing%20with%20thoughts%20of%20ending%20my%20life.%20I%20would%20always%20look%20at%20it%20as%20a%20relief%20from%20this%20silent%20suffering.%20Soon%20enough%2C%20thoughts%20of%20harming%20myself%20and%20suicide%20became%20stronger%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20professor%20in%20his%20college%20who%20noticed%20Raj%E2%80%99s%20behaviour%20and%20advised%20him%20to%20see%20the%20campus%20therapist.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20that%20time%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F315631%2Fbengaluru-punita-mittal-mahak-maheshwari-soulup-mental-health-online-support-platform%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseeing%20a%20therapist%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20like%20a%20leap%20of%20faith%20for%20me%20as%20I%20had%20made%20up%20my%20mind%20that%20there%20was%20no%20end%20to%20the%20suffering.%20In%20that%20two-hour%20long%20session%2C%20I%20just%20vented%20out.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20therapist%20was%20a%20great%20listener%20and%20he%20helped%20me%20realise%20that%20I%20have%20to%20talk%20through%20my%20issues%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20So%20Raj%20continued%20to%20visit%20the%20therapist%20to%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F317358%2Fmodel-dinesh-mohan-silver-fox-narrates-battle-with-eating-disorder-and-depression%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20fight%20depression%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CFighting%20depression%20is%20not%20a%20linear%20journey%3B%20it%20is%20not%20like%20you%20are%20in%20and%20then%20out%20of%20it.%20It%20is%20a%20combination%20of%20relapses.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98There%20is%20light%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20tunnel%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCxasLGkv9Ni%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCxasLGkv9Ni%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%