20DRS%20call%20which%20went%20against%20him%20in%20his%20side's%20World%20Cup%20match%20against%20Sri%20Lanka%20and%20has%20called%20for%20more%20%26quot%3Baccountability%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20system%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report.%20In%20the%20match%2C%20which%20Australia%20won%20by%20five%20wickets%20in%20Lucknow%20on%20Monday%2C%20Warner%20fell%20LBW%20to%20Sri%20Lanka%20pacer%20Dilshan%20Madushanka.%20The%20left-hander%20went%20for%20review%20but%20the%20DRS%20call%20went%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20on-field%20umpire%2C%20who%20had%20originally%20given%20him%20out.%20The%20prolific%20southpaw%2C%20who%20was%20batting%20on%2011%2C%20left%20the%20ground%20fuming.%20He%20was%20seen%20smashing%20his%20bat%20against%20his%20pad%20and%20turned%20back%20to%20yell%20towards%20the%20wicket%20as%20he%20walked%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWarner%20said%20he%20wanted%20greater%20transparency%20on%20how%20DRS%20decisions%20were%20adjudicated.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20never%20had%20Hawk-Eye%20come%20in%20and%20explain%20to%20us%20how%20the%20technology%20actually%20works%2C%20it's%20just%20for%20the%20TV%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2036-year-old%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20'cricket.com.au'%20after%20Australia's%20five-wicket%20win%20over%20Sri%20Lanka%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20they%20could%20come%20in%20and%20explain%20to%20us%20how%20it%20works%2C%20then%20sometimes%20we%20might%20(choose)%20not%20to%20refer%20or%20to%20refer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20Warner%20suggested%20that%20the%20ball-tracking%20did%20not%20match%20what%20he%20saw%20on%20the%20ground's%20replay%20screen%20after%20he%20called%20for%20the%20review.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20asked%20Joel%20(field%20umpire)%20when%20I%20was%20out%20there%20just%20what%20happened%2C%20why%20did%20he%20give%20it%20out.%20He%20said%20the%20ball%20was%20swinging%20back%20so%20to%20his%20credit%2C%20if%20he%20thinks%20that%20then%20that's%20why%20he's%20given%20a%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B(The%20ball)%20kept%20low%20and%20normally%20when%20something%20hits%20me%20on%20the%20leg%20on%20the%20outside%2C%20I%20know%20it's%20pretty%20much%20going%20down%20leg.%20So%20he%20(Wilson)%20said%20it%20was%20swinging%20back%2C%20(but)%20from%20my%20perspective%20on%20the%20replay%2C%20it%20wasn't%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20see%20the%20replay%20of%20how%20it%20unfolded%20you%20get%20a%20little%20bit%20annoyed%2C%20(but)%20that's%20out%20of%20our%20control.%26quot%3B%20Warner%20also%20felt%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report%2C%20that%20ball-tracking%20verdicts%20were%20%26quot%3Btaking%20a%20lot%20longer%20than%20what%20it%20would%20be%20in%20Australia%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Decision%20Review%20System%20was%20introduced%20in%202008%2C%20ahead%20of%20Warner's%20international%20debut%20in%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20moment%2C%20we%20seem%20to%20be%20waiting%20for%20(ball-tracking)%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Warner.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20as%20a%20player%20you%20get%20more%20frustrated%20because%20you%20think%3A%20'did%20they%20line%20it%20up%2C%20what's%20the%20impact%20points%2C%20how%20many%20impact%20points%20are%20there%20before%20it%20goes%20on'.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20England%2C%20the%20ball%20bounces%20and%20it%20actually%20moves%20once%20it's%20bounced%2C%20not%20just%20off%20the%20seam%20but%20in%20the%20air%20it%20can%20move%2C%20so%20there's%20just%20little%20things%20that%20as%20a%20player%20you%20get%20frustrated%20because%20there's%20no%20explanation%20%E2%80%A6%20but%20there%20has%20to%20be%20some%20accountability.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ICC%20has%20not%20announced%20any%20sanction%20for%20Warner's%20outburst%20but%20he%20insisted%20his%20furious%20reaction%20was%20due%20to%20his%20frustration%20with%20the%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20sprayed%20out%20loud%20in%20frustration%20pretty%20much%20just%20(to)%20myself%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Warner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697613660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fhep1g85g_david-warner-drs_625x300_18_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fdid-they-line-it-up-taking-longer-than-david-warner-reignites-cricket-world-cup-2023-drs-row-4491543%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20a%20report%2C%20Warner%20suggested%20that%20the%20ball-tracking%20did%20not%20match%20what%20he%20saw%20on%20the%20ground's%20replay%20screen%20after%20he%20called%20for%20the%20review.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A75%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fdid-they-line-it-up-taking-longer-than-david-warner-reignites-cricket-world-cup-2023-drs-row-4491543%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fdid-they-line-it-up-taking-longer-than-david-warner-reignites-cricket-world-cup-2023-drs-row-4491543%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fdid-they-line-it-up-taking-longer-than-david-warner-reignites-cricket-world-cup-2023-drs-row-4491543%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Union%20Government%20to%20Prohibit%20Sugar%20Exports%20Again%20This%20Season%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F26103523%2Fsugar-485055_1280.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Union%20government%20will%20continue%20to%20prohibit%20sugar%20exports%20this%20season%20(October%202023%20to%20September%202024)%20after%20a%20drop%20in%20production%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20rain.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20their%20top%20priorities%20are%20to%20produce%20ethanol%20and%20to%20have%20an%20adequate%20supply%20available%20in%20the%20domestic%20market%2C%20especially%20in%20an%20election%20year%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Feconomy%2Fagri-business%2Fgovt-to-prohibit-sugar-export-to-protect-domestic-market%2Farticle67429716.ece%5C%22%3Ethe%20Hindu%20BusinessLine%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20notification%20issued%20on%20October%2028%2C%202022%2C%20the%20Directorate%20General%20of%20Foreign%20Trade%20said%20it%20would%20be%20mandatory%20for%20exporters%20to%20have%20a%20prior%20permit%20from%20the%20food%20ministry.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20restriction%20on%20sugar%20exports%20would%20be%20in%20place%20until%20further%20orders%20or%20October%2031%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Director%20General%20of%20Foreign%20Trade%20will%20notify%20the%20sugar%20export%20policy%20this%20week%20as%20the%20validity%20of%20the%20previous%20notification%20expires%20on%20October%2031%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20official%20source%20said.%20While%20there%20will%20be%20a%20continuation%20of%20the%20earlier%20policy%2C%20there%20are%20two%20likely%20changes%20this%20time%20%E2%80%93%20there%20will%20be%20no%20deadline%2C%20and%20organic%20export%20will%20not%20be%20exempted%20from%20restriction%2C%20sources%20told%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20restriction%20will%20halt%20shipments%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fmarkets%2Fcommodities%2Findia-set-ban-sugar-exports-first-time-7-years-2023-08-23%2F%5C%22%3Efirst%20time%20in%20seven%20years.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20restricted%20the%20amount%20of%20exports%20during%202022-23%20as%20well%2C%20allowing%20mills%20to%20export%20only%206.1%20million%20tonnes%20of%20sugar%20after%20letting%20them%20sell%20a%20record%2011.1%20million%20tonnes%20the%20season%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20news%20agency%20Reuters%20in%20August%2C%20a%20government%20source%20who%20asked%20not%20to%20be%20named%20in%20line%20with%20official%20rules%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20primary%20focus%20is%20to%20fulfill%20local%20sugar%20requirements%20and%20produce%20ethanol%20from%20surplus%20sugarcane.%20For%20the%20upcoming%20season%2C%20we%20will%20not%20have%20enough%20sugar%20to%20allocate%20for%20export%20quotas.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThough%20it%20is%20not%20a%20ban%2C%20it%20has%20the%20same%20meaning%20if%20permits%20are%20not%20issued%20for%20export.%20However%2C%20an%20early%20announcement%20will%20help%20mills%20plan%20how%20much%20sugarcane%20to%20be%20diverted%20to%20make%20sugar%20and%20how%20much%20for%20ethanol%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Feconomy%2Fagri-business%2Fgovt-to-prohibit-sugar-export-to-protect-domestic-market%2Farticle67429716.ece%5C%22%3Ean%20industry%20expert%20said.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697613610000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F26103523%2Fsugar-485055_1280.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftrade%2Funion-government-to-prohibit-sugar-exports-again-this-season%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20there%20will%20be%20a%20continuation%20of%20the%20earlier%20policy%2C%20there%20are%20two%20likely%20changes%20this%20time%20%E2%80%93%20there%20will%20be%20no%20deadline%2C%20and%20organic%20export%20will%20not%20be%20exempted%20from%20restriction.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftrade%2Funion-government-to-prohibit-sugar-exports-again-this-season%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22At%20least%20189%20decomposed%20bodies%20removed%20from%20'green'%20US%20funeral%20home%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697613180000%2C%22visual