c%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F02102630%2F1156px-Supreme_Court_of_India_01.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20majority%20of%20people%20in%20our%20cultures%2C%20a%20marriage%20has%20a%20husband%20and%20a%20wife.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20many%20people%2C%20the%20absence%20of%20one%20entity%20out%20of%20these%20two%20does%20not%20make%20it%20a%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20exactly%20what%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20seems%20to%20have%20based%20its%20verdict%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFrom%20what%20I%20understood%2C%20the%20apex%20court%2C%20with%20a%203%3A2%20majority%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fmarriage-equality-supreme-court-decision%5C%22%3Eis%20against%20the%20marriage%20or%20even%20legal%20union%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20people%20having%20the%20same%20gender.%20This%20in%20spite%20of%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20comment%20saying%20same%20sex%20union%20is%20%E2%80%9Cnatural%20and%20old.%E2%80%9D%20And%20there%20is%20nothing%20%E2%80%9Curban%20and%20elite%E2%80%9D%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20top%20court%2C%20spouses%20have%20to%20be%20a%20man%20and%20a%20woman%20%E2%80%93%20whether%20they%20are%20cisgender%20(affirm%20the%20gender%20they%20are%20born%20with)%20or%20trans%20gender%20(not%20affirming%20to%20the%20gender%20they%20have%20been%20assigned%20at%20birth.%20However%2C%20being%20in%20a%20same%20sex%20relationship%20is%20neither%20forbidden%20nor%20illegal%20according%20to%20this%20judgement.%20So%20same-sex%20partners%20can%20cohabit%2C%20but%20will%20not%20have%20the%20same%20rights%20as%20a%20spouse.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20cannot%20adopt%20together%20as%20a%20couple%20and%20have%20no%20rights%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20property%2C%20inheritance%20or%20even%20insurance.%20The%20judges%20also%20refused%20to%20annul%20or%20tweak%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Special%20Marriage%20Act%20(SMA)%20to%20include%20non-heterosexual%20couples%20within%20its%20fold.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20apex%20court%20said%20that%20queer%20couples%20have%20a%20right%20to%20cohabit%20without%20any%20threat%20of%20violence%2C%20coercion%20of%20interference.%20The%20judges%20also%20unanimously%20gave%20a%20go%20ahead%20to%20a%20high-powered%20committee%20proposed%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20examine%20the%20concerns%20of%20same-sex%20couples%20and%20take%20corrective%20measures.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGender%20rights%20activists%20are%20trying%20to%20find%20a%20silver%20lining%20in%20the%20verdict%2C%20as%20the%20apex%20court%20has%20tried%20to%20further%20decriminalise%20living%20with%20same-sex%20partners%20through%20it.%20As%20one%20of%20the%20judges%20has%20said%20that%20both%20heterosexual%20and%20homosexual%20unions%20have%20to%20be%20looked%20as%20%60two%20sides%20of%20the%20same%20coin%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAgain%20however%20one%20feels%2C%20the%20apex%20court%20has%20again%20stopped%20short%20of%20taking%20a%20clear%20stand%20by%20saying%20only%20government%20and%20parliament%20can%20make%20laws%20and%20legalise%20same-sex%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELike%20many%20times%20in%20the%20past%20the%20verdict%20seems%20to%20be%20majoritarian%20in%20more%20than%20one%20ways.%20It%20goes%20totally%20in%20favour%20of%20those%20opposing%20the%20marriage%20and%20legal%20sanctions%20of%20such%20a%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20honourable%20judges%20have%20not%20opposed%20same%20sex%20unions%2C%20at%20the%20same%20time%20they%20have%20provided%20no%20alternative%20to%20bring%20it%20under%20the%20purview%20of%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20courts%2C%20there%20will%20be%20nothing%20formal%20about%20these%20relationships.%20So%20to%20my%20understanding%20till%20the%20parliament%20makes%20some%20regulations%20is%20that%20there%20will%20be%20no%20protection%2C%20no%20divorce%20proceedings%2C%20no%20alimony.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20is%20paramount%20in%20a%20country%20like%20ours%20where%20for%20a%20majority%20of%20population%2C%20social%20sanction%20for%20a%20relationship%20comes%20only%20after%20marriage.%20There%20is%20also%20a%20minority%20perception%20which%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20believe%20in%20any%20kind%20of%20formal%20bond%20for%20two%20consenting%20adults%20to%20live%20together.%20This%20hearts%E2%80%99%20calling%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20is%20not%20the%20view%20of%20majority%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20our%20parents%E2%80%99%20generation%20and%20even%20many%20in%20the%20current%20generation%20%E2%80%93%20only%20marriage%20can%20mean%20commitment%20and%20stability.%20Although%20I%20believe%20for%20a%20marriage%20to%20work%2C%20hearts%20have%20to%20be%20in%20harmony%2C%20that%20view%20might%20not%20be%20shared%20by%20society%20in%20general.%20If%20this%20verdict%20was%20otherwise%2C%20it%20would%20have%20given%20partners%20that%20place%20in%20society%20which%20is%20rightfully%20theirs%20and%20also%20given%20reasons%20for%20parents%20to%20agree%20to%20such%20unions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20agree%20with%20this%20moralistic%20view%20or%20care%20for%20social%20approval%2C%20consider%20the%20safety%20of%20partners%20in%20a%20relationship%20which%20is%20not%20protected%20by%20law%3F%20When%20marriage%20is%20not%20legal%2C%20families%20can%20prevail%20at%20any%20time%2C%20putting%20the%20safety%20of%20partners%20in%20such%20a%20union%20at%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20about%20domestic%20violence%3F%20Are%20we%20saying%20that%20violence%20and%20abuse%20are%20only%20prevalent%20in%20a%20marriage%20between%20opposite%20genders%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20about%20financial%20security%3F%20If%20a%20partner%20in%20a%20same-sex%20union%20has%20an%20untimely%20death%20and%20the%20living%20partner%20is%20not%20earning%2C%20how%20is%20depriving%20the%20dependent%20partner%20of%20financial%20security%20justified%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESame-sex%20couples%20will%20have%20no%20right%20to%20each%20others%E2%80%99%20property%20even%20if%20they%20are%20together%20for%20a%20lifetime%20unless%20they%20leave%20a%20will.%20A%20same-sex%20couple%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20start%20a%20family%20legally.%20Single%20parent%20adoption%20will%20be%20difficult%20for%20them%2C%20one%20assumes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20one%20wonders%20what%20safety%20blanket%20the%20verdict%20is%20providing%20at%20all.%20Years%20ago%20when%20I%20was%20covering%20health%20and%20HIV%2FAIDS%20was%20a%20subject%20that%20deeply%20interested%20me%2C%20the%20discrimination%20against%20the%20LGBTQ%20community%20was%20jarring.%20Abuse%20and%20rape%20in%20the%20name%20of%20law%20was%20rampant.%20The%20community%20is%20more%20vocal%20now%20than%20it%20ever%20was%20in%20the%20country%20but%20it%20is%20only%20laws%20and%20court%20verdicts%20which%20can%20provide%20protection%20without%20loopholes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20citizen%20of%20the%20country%20is%20free%20to%20do%20anything%2C%20live%20any%20life%20as%20long%20as%20he%2Fshe%2Fthey%20are%20not%20posing%20a%20threat%20to%20others%20but%20does%20this%20verdict%20give%20that%20right%20to%20same-sex%20couples%3F%20Will%20the%20verdict%20discourage%20closet%20behaviour%20or%20forced%20marriages%3F%20The%20verdict%20puts%20the%20onus%20of%20living%20a%20safe%20life%20on%20the%20community%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20honourable%20courts%20have%20to%20come%20out%20of%20the%20mode%20of%20verdicts%20aimed%20for%20the%20satisfaction%20of%20the%20majority%20and%20take%20some%20unpopular%20decisions%20for%20the%20larger%20good%20of%20some%20marginalised%20communities%20as%20well.%20This%20is%2C%20again%2C%20one%20of%20the%20strings%20of%20judgements%20where%20majority%20opinion%20wins%20over%20logic.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EToufiq%20Rashid%20is%20a%20journalist%20who%20has%20covered%20the%20Kashmir%20conflict%2C%20health%20and%20wellbeing%20for%20top%20Indian%20newspapers%20for%20nearly%20two%20decades.%20She%20now%