of%20our%20country%2C%20Shri%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20boosted%20the%20courage%20of%20our%20scientists%20and%20asked%20them%20to%20try%20once%20more.%20All%20scientists%20together%20tried%20and%20improved%20their%20work%20by%20learning%20from%20past%20experience%20so%20that%20the%20%E2%80%98lander%E2%80%99%20could%20successfully%20land%20on%20the%20lunar%20surface%20by%20the%20launcher%2C%E2%80%9D%20read%20an%20interactive%20module%20for%20nursery%20and%20Class%20I%20and%20II%20children%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fncert-module-credits-pm-modi-for-success-of-chandrayaan-3-ignores-isros-track-record%2Fcid%2F1974042%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20module%20carries%20pictures%20of%20Modi%20joining%20the%20live%20telecast%20of%20the%20launch%20as%20well%20as%20his%20interaction%20with%20the%20scientists%20at%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%20headquarters%20in%20Bengaluru%20along%20with%20the%20Chandrayaan-3%20on%20the%20moon%E2%80%99s%20surface.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20special%20reading%20materials%20on%20the%20Chandrayaan%20mission%20were%20released%20by%20Union%20education%20minister%20Dharmendra%20Pradhan%20at%20a%20programme%20in%20Delhi%20on%20Monday%2C%20October%2017%2C%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20ISRO%20chairman%20S.P.%20Somanath.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20leadership%20of%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20Prime%20Minister%20Shri%20Narendra%20Modi%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20the%20triumph%20of%20Chandrayaan-3%20and%20landed%20our%20country%E2%80%99s%20name%20on%20the%20surface%20of%20the%20moon%2C%E2%80%9D%20one%20of%20the%20modules%20lavishes%20praise%20on%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESeveral%20space%20experts%20who%20spoke%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Edescribed%20the%20wording%20as%20problematic%2C%20as%20it%2C%20according%20to%20them%2C%20gives%20an%20impression%20that%20the%20Chandrayaan-3%20mission%20was%20possible%20only%20because%20of%20Modi.%20This%2C%20they%20say%2C%20goes%20against%20the%20ISRO%E2%80%99s%20track%20record%20of%20bouncing%20back%20from%20its%20failures.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETracing%20the%20history%20of%20ISRO%2C%20a%20space%20expert%20recalled%20that%20a%20Satellite%20Launch%20Vehicle%20launched%20by%20the%20agency%20failed%20in%201979%2C%20but%20it%20attempted%20the%20exercise%20again%20the%20next%20year%20and%20emerged%20successful.%20Similarly%2C%20after%20the%20Augmented%20Satellite%20Launch%20Vehicle%20failed%20in%201987%2C%20ISRO%20made%20it%20successful%20the%20next%20year%2C%20in%201988.%20It%20was%20later%20successfully%20launched%20in%201994.%20The%20same%20thing%20happened%20with%20ISRO%E2%80%99s%20Polar%20Satellite%20Launch%20Vehicle%2C%20which%20failed%20in%201993%20but%20was%20successfully%20launched%20in%20the%20next%20attempt%20in%20a%20year%20in%201994.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20every%20failure%2C%20ISRO%20never%20gave%20up.%20However%2C%20the%20text%20in%20the%20NCERT%20module%20creates%20the%20impression%20that%20Chandrayaan-3%20was%20launched%20only%20after%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20asked%20the%20scientists%20to%20try%20once%20more.%20This%20may%20not%20be%20matching%20Isro%E2%80%99s%20track%20record%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20space%20expert%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20module%2C%20meant%20for%20middle%20school%20children%2C%20one%20can%20see%20mythology%20mixed%20up%20with%20space%20science.%20%E2%80%9CDid%20scientific%20achievement%20happen%20only%20now%3F%E2%80%A6%20Literature%20tells%20us%20that%20it%20can%20be%20traced%20back%20through%20Vymaanika%20Shastra%3A%20%E2%80%98Science%20of%20Aeronautics%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20reveals%20that%20our%20country%20had%20the%20knowledge%20of%20flying%20vehicles%20in%20these%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20module%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20goes%20on%20to%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Vedas%2C%20the%20oldest%20of%20Indian%20texts%2C%20makes%20a%20mention%20of%20various%20gods%20being%20transported%20on%20wheeled%20chariots%20pulled%20by%20animals%2C%20usually%20horses%2C%20but%20these%20chariots%20could%20also%20fly.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20module%20also%20makes%20a%20reference%20to%20Pushpak%20Vimaan%2C%20a%20floating%20chariot%20mentioned%20in%20the%20Ramayana.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20created%20by%20Vishwakarma%2C%20the%20chief%20architect%20of%20gods%2C%20out%20of%20the%20dust%20from%20the%20Sun%20for%20Brahma.%20Brahma%20gave%20it%20to%20Kuber.%20When%20Ravana%20took%20over%20Lanka%20from%20Kuber%2C%20it%20was%20used%20by%20Ravana%20as%20his%20personal%20vehicle.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697607221000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18105527%2FF8pgm08bQAA7BaK.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fncert-reading-modules-credit-modi-for-success-of-chandrayaan-3-mix-space-science-with-vedas%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Several%20space%20experts%20say%20the%20special%20supplementary%20reading%20modules%20by%20NCERT%20on%20the%20Chandrayaan%20mission%20do%20injustice%20to%20ISRO%20and%20its%20scientists%2C%20who%20have%20over%20the%20years%20bounced%20back%20from%20every%20failure%20in%20their%20way.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A29%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fncert-reading-modules-credit-modi-for-success-of-chandrayaan-3-mix-space-science-with-vedas%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20accuses%20China's%20fighter%20jets%20of%20'dangerous'%20manoeuvres%20against%20its%20military%20aircraft%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697607060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F10%2F768x432%2Fskynews-us-china-aircraft-pentagon_6325257.jpg%3F20231018065009%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fus-accuses-chinas-fighter-jets-of-dangerous-manoeuvres-against-its-military-aircraft-12986730%22