%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20man%2C%20identified%20as%20Maayank%20Tiwari%20from%20Vadodara%2C%20claimed%20to%20be%20a%20director%20(government%20advisory)%20and%20was%20collecting%20crores%20of%20rupees%20by%20either%20threatening%20people%20or%20using%20the%20PMO%20tag%20to%20%E2%80%9Csettle%20disputes%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20flagged%20by%20Chirag%20Panchal%2C%20an%20undersecretary%20with%20the%20PMO%2C%20to%20the%20CBI%2C%20which%20booked%20Tiwari.%20Tiwari%20threatened%20the%20managing%20director%20of%20of%20Dr%20Agarwal%E2%80%99s%20and%20forced%20him%20to%20settle%20a%20dispute%20of%20over%20Rs%2016.43%20crore%20with%20two%20Indore-based%20doctors.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F17212615%2FUnknown.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221008%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F17212615%2FUnknown.jpeg%201008w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F17212615%2FUnknown-252x300.jpeg%20252w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F17212615%2FUnknown-860x1024.jpeg%20860w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-680524%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPhoto%20courtesy%3A%20Vibes%20of%20India%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news18.com%2Findia%2Fcbi-books-man-for-posing-as-pmo-official-threatening-promoters-of-hospital-chain-8622273.html%5C%22%3Enews%20agency%20PTI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Dr%20Agarwal%E2%80%99s%20entered%20into%20an%20agreement%20with%20two%20doctors%20who%20ran%20the%20Indore-based%20hospital%20to%20join%20the%20franchise%20for%20which%20over%20Rs%2016%20crore%20was%20paid.%20The%20Indore%20hospital%20allegedly%20started%20violating%20the%20terms%20of%20the%20agreement%20which%20resulted%20in%20a%20dispute%20and%20Dr%20Agarwal%E2%80%99s%20wanted%20their%20money%20back%20and%20the%20termination%20of%20the%20agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20appointed%20an%20arbitrator%20to%20negotiate%20a%20settlement%2C%20and%20the%20arbitrator%20in%20an%20interim%20injunction%20asked%20the%20Indore-based%20hospital%20to%20deposit%20Rs%2016.43%20crore%20within%20four%20weeks.%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20dispute%2C%20the%20promoters%20of%20Dr%20Agarwal%E2%80%99s%20started%20getting%20messages%20and%20calls%20from%20Tiwari%20to%20forget%20the%20alleged%20dues%20and%20settle%20the%20matter%20with%20the%20doctors%20running%20the%20Indore%20hospital%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20PTI%20report%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20second%20time%20in%20less%20than%20100%20days%20that%20Maayank%20Tiwari%20has%20posed%20as%20a%20top%20PMO%20official.%20In%20June%2C%20he%20threatened%20a%20trustee%20of%20a%20private%20university%20in%20Vadodara%20and%20was%20tried%20to%20force%20a%20prestigious%20school%20to%20grant%20admission%20to%20two%20children%20who%20he%20claimed%20were%20his%20friend%E2%80%99s%20children.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20he%20spelt%20his%20name%20as%20Mayank.%20In%20the%20latest%20case%2C%20he%20has%20added%20an%20%E2%80%9Ca%E2%80%9D%20to%20his%20first%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20trustee%20of%20the%20school%20became%20suspicious%2C%20he%20alerted%20the%20police.%20The%20Gujarat%20police%20arrested%20Tiwari%20in%20June%20and%20said%20that%20was%20charging%20money%20for%20admissions%20and%20posing%20as%20a%20PMO%20official%20to%20threaten%20schools%20and%20college%20owners.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20exploits%20were%20minor%20compared%20to%20Kiran%20Patel%2C%20an%20Ahmedabad%20resident%20who%20posed%20as%20additional%20director%20(strategy%20and%20campaigns)%20of%20the%20PMO%2C%20bragged%20about%20his%20RSS%20connections%20and%20availed%20of%20Z%20security%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20to%20undertake%20%E2%80%9Cofficial%20visits%E2%80%9D.%20His%20wife%20also%20made%20similar%20claims.%20The%20couple%20is%20currently%20in%20jail.%20There%20are%20eight%20complaints%20against%20Kiran%20Patel%20and%20his%20wife%20for%20threatening%20people%20using%20the%20PMO%20tag%20and%20extorting%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPatel%20and%20his%20wife%20were%20also%20accused%20in%20several%20land%20fraud%20cases.%20In%20one%20case%2C%20he%20allegedly%20cheated%20a%20person%20of%20Rs%2080%20lakh%20as%20commission%20claiming%20he%20would%20settle%20the%20land%20dispute.%20He%20cheated%20a%20former%20BJP%20MLA%20for%20land%20and%20construction%20activities.%20Patel%20visited%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20four%20times%20in%20six%20months%20claiming%20he%20was%20on%20official%20duty.%20He%20also%20toured%20top%20security%20and%20other%20government%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EInputs%20from%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vibesofindia.com%2Fone-more-fake-pmo-director-caught-from-gujarat%2F%5C%22%3EVibes%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20were%20used%20in%20this%20article%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697559524000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2F15122315%2FSouth-Block_Wikimedia.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcbi-book-fake-pmo-official-vadodara-mayank-tiwari%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20man%2C%20identified%20as%20Maayank%20Tiwari%20from%20Vadodara%2C%20claimed%20to%20be%20a%20director%20(government%20advisory)%20and%20was%20collecting%20crores%20of%20rupees%20by%20either%20threatening%20people%20or%20using%20the%20PMO%20tag%20to%20%E2%80%9Csettle%20disputes%E2%80%9D.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcbi-book-fake-pmo-official-vadodara-mayank-tiwari%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22