wire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fmaldives-president-elect-calls-for-sovereignty-india-stresses-cooperation-on-security-challenges%5C%22%3Ecalled%20on%20the%20president-elect%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20October%204%20and%20handed%20over%20a%20letter%20from%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Maldivian%20readout%20of%20that%20meeting%20didn%E2%80%99t%20explicitly%20refer%20to%20the%20controversy%20over%20the%20presence%20of%20Indian%20troops%2C%20but%20that%20Muizzu%20would%20like%20to%20%E2%80%9Crestore%20relations%20with%20India%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20respect%20for%20sovereignty%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDJWBSdWFo0Q%5C%22%3Erecent%20interview%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20Al%20Jazeera%20television%2C%20Muizzu%20stated%20that%20he%20had%20personally%20raised%20the%20matter%20with%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20actually%20met%20with%20the%20Indian%20high%20commissioner%20few%20days%20ago%20during%20the%20transition%20period%20and%20during%20that%20meeting%20itself%2C%20I%20had%20mentioned%20that%20we%20need%20this%20to%20be%20our%20top%20most%20priority.%20They%20have%20positively%20noted%20that.%20And%20they%20have%20said%20that%20they%20will%20work%20together%20with%20us%20to%20find%20a%20way%20forward%20on%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Maldives%20is%20currently%20going%20through%20a%20transition%20period%2C%20with%20Muizzu%E2%80%99s%20term%20set%20to%20start%20on%20November%2017%20with%20a%20formal%20swearing-in%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAsked%20when%20he%20would%20request%20India%20to%20remove%20the%20troops%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CDefinitely%20day%20one.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20follow-up%20question%20on%20the%20timeline%20for%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20troops%2C%20Muizzu%20replied%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6if%20it%20is%20possible%20within%20the%20first%20week%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20how%20serio