ry%20cooperation%20with%20China%20to%20balance%20with%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENoting%20that%20half%20of%20Maldives%E2%80%99s%20external%20debt%20was%20from%20Indian%20borrowed%20loans%2C%20Muizzu%20said%20that%20he%20had%20also%20raised%20it%20with%20the%20Indian%20envoy%2C%20who%20had%20been%20positive%20about%20it.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20a%20way%20to%20refinance%20and%20if%20possible%20waive%20(it%20off)%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20whether%20India%20would%20have%20any%20incentive%20to%20remove%20foreign%20troops%20when%20the%20Maldives%20was%20asking%20for%20debt%20waiver%2C%20Muizzu%20replied%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20clearly%20said%20that%20in%20the%20very%20first%20meeting%20that%20I%20had%20with%20the%20high%20commissioner.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20stated%20that%20India%20didn%E2%80%99t%20seem%20inclined%20to%20diminish%20its%20development%20assistance%20or%20investment%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20state.%20%E2%80%9CI%20really%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20they%20will%20do%20that.%20They%20may%20be%20interested%20in%20giving%20more%20lines%20of%20credit%20to%20invest%20in%20the%20tourism%20sector.%E2%80%9D%20Muizzu%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20the%20Maldives%20always%20had%20a%20good%20relationship%20with%20India%2C%20he%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20it%20to%20be%20any%20different.%20It%20is%20only%20the%20sovereignty%20issue%E2%80%A6%20I%20will%20definitely%20be%20positive%20towards%20development%20assistance%20from%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20that%20Maldives%20would%20also%20like%20to%20have%20close%20ties%20with%20China%20as%20with%20all%20other%20countries%2C%20but%20also%20noted%20that%20Beijing%20never%20extended%20its%20assistance%20in%20a%20way%20that%20would%20interfere%20in%20the%20internal%20affairs%20or%20impact%20the%20sovereignty%20of%20Maldives.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20Indian%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20had%20talked%20about%20the%20need%20to%20work%20closely%20on%20security%20challenges%20after%20Muizzu%20raised%20the%20issue%20of%20Indian%20troops.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20I%20would%20say%E2%80%A6%20the%20focus%20of%20our%20partnership%20with%20the%20Maldives%20has%20always%20been%20on%20capacity%20building%20and%20working%20together%20to%20address%20our%20shared%20challenges%20and%20priorities%2C%20including%20security%20challenges%20and%20priorities.%20As%20neighbours%2C%20we%20need%20to%20collaborate%20closely%20to%20address%20these%20challenges%20confronting%20our%20region%2C%20such%20as%20transnational%20crimes%20and%20Humanitarian%20and%20Disaster%20Relief%20situations.%20We%20look%20forward%20to%20engaging%20with%20the%20new%20administration%20in%20the%20Maldives%20with%20all%20these%20issues%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20MEA%20spokesperson%20at%20a%20media%20briefing%20on%20October%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697554249000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F17194015%2FF8cxCy0agAA1r64.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fmaldives-mohamed-muizzu-indian-troops-top-priority%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mohamed%20Muizzu%20told%20Al%20Jazeera%20that%20he%20would%20request%20India%20to%20remove%20troops%20on%20%26quot%3Bday%20one%E2%80%9D%20and%20hope%20that%20they%20would%20be%20withdrawn%C2%A0within%20the%20first%20week%20of%20his%20presidency%2C%20which%20will%20begin%20on%20November%2017.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fmaldives-mohamed-muizzu-indian-troops-top-priority%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20threat%20of%20another%20Brussels%20attack%20has%20subsided%20-%20but%20the%20ripples%20of%20shock%20are%20significant%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697553120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F10%2F768x432%2F