%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexclusive%20pieces%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20mosaic%20and%20wood%20art%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20come%20cheap.%20Also%2C%20since%20only%20the%20two%20of%20them%20handle%20the%20creative%20aspect%20of%20the%20business%2C%20they%20cannot%20make%20products%20in%20large%20numbers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20there%20are%20two%20other%20people%20in%20their%20workshop%20who%20help%20with%20the%20mosaic%20works%20along%20with%20three%20freelancing%20carpenters%20and%20polishers%20for%20the%20woodwork.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20wall%20arts%20from%20their%20studio%20start%20at%20Rs%202%2C000-2%2C500%20per%20square%20foot%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20intricacy%20of%20design.%20The%20price%20of%20a%20driftwood%20centre%20table%20ranges%20from%20Rs%2018%2C000%20to%20Rs%2040%2C000%20which%20depends%20on%20the%20size%20and%20the%20quality%20of%20wood.%20Mosaic%20garden%20tables%2C%20two%20feet%20in%20diameter%2C%20cost%20Rs%2012%2C500.%20Floor%20lamps%20are%20priced%20at%20Rs%207%2C000-10%2C000.%20Planters%20range%20from%20Rs%205%2C000-15%2C000%2C%20depending%20on%20size.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYohann%20has%20a%20residence-cum-studio%20in%20Bandra%20where%20clients%20can%20take%20a%20look%20at%20the%20products.%20The%20company%20gets%20orders%20from%20across%20India.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20fact%2C%20more%20than%20half%20of%20our%20clientele%20is%20outside%20Mumbai.%20Our%20products%20are%20large%20and%20meant%20for%20large%20spaces.%20Around%2060%20percent%20of%20our%20pieces%20are%20custom-made%20while%2040%20percent%20is%20from%20an%20inventory.%20We%20are%20now%20looking%20to%20grow%20the%20business%20through%20projects%20to%20do%20up%20villas%20and%20homes%20by%20collaborating%20with%20interior%20designers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20537px)%20100vw%2C%20537px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDriftwood-side-table_11zon-1697535566.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22537%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20side-table%20made%20with%20using%20a%20piece%20of%20driftwood.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDriftwood-side-table_11zon-1697535566.jpg%20537w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDriftwood-side-table_11zon-1697535566-262x300.jpg%20262w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDriftwood-side-table_11zon-1697535566-500x572.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDriftwood-side-table_11zon-1697535566-150x172.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332390%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22614%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20side-table%20made%20with%20using%20a%20piece%20of%20driftwood.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECreating%20unique%20products%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20their%20mosaic%20pieces%20are%20indeed%20eye-catching%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20their%20driftwood%20tables%20and%20other%20wares%20that%20are%20equally%20beautiful%20too.%20Driftwood%20is%20basically%20the%20wood%20that%20has%20been%20washed%20ashore%20onto%20a%20beach%20from%20the%20sea%2C%20lake%20or%20a%20river.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDriftwood%20as%20well%20as%20upcycled%20wood%20come%20with%20a%20history.%20The%20character%2C%20texture%2C%20grain%2C%20and%20shape%20work%20as%20an%20inspiration%20for%20us.%20It%20requires%20a%20keen%20eye%2C%20and%20an%20active%20imagination%20to%20visualise%20and%20conceptualise%20the%20potential%20of%20every%20piece.%20And%20each%20one%20is%20different.%20Some%20make%20great%20lamps%2C%20some%20ingenious%20tabletops%2C%20some%20rustic%20benches.%20They%20can%20be%20used%20within%20the%20home%20and%20outdoors%20too.%C2%A0No%20two%20pieces%20are%20the%20same%20and%20the%20challenge%20is%20always%20to%20create%20something%20different.%20It%20is%20the%20joy%20and%20immense%20satisfaction%20of%20creating%20art%20from%20waste%20that%20drives%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Naomi.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDriftwood%20has%20to%20undergo%20a%20rigorous%20process%20before%20it%20can%20be%20worked%20with.%20It%20involves%20scrubbing%20and%20cleaning%20the%20piece%2C%20bleaching%20it%20over%20a%20period%20of%20weeks%20to%20remove%20the%20insects%20as%20well%20as%20lighten%20the%20wood%C2%A0tones.%20Then%20it%20is%20protected%20from%20termites%20and%20kept%20out%20in%20the%20sun%20to%20dry%20thoroughly%2C%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20entire%20day%20is%20spent%20in%20my%20workshop%2C%20especially%20if%20we%20have%20hard%20deadlines.%20At%20times%2C%20day%20creeps%20into%20night.%20Sometimes%2C%20I%20even%20forget%20to%20eat.%20I%20hire%20more%20hands%20on%20a%20daily%20wage%20basis%20if%20I%20need%20extra%20assistance.%20While%20I%20lay%20the%20creative%20groundwork%20for%20a%20piece%2C%20the%20machine%20work%20is%20handled%20by%20my%20team%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20clients%20like%20The%20Dignity%20Foundation%20for%20the%20elderly%2C%20who%20got%20a%20piece%20made%20for%20their%20newest%20project%20in%20Neral%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20and%20the%20LV%20Prasad%20eye%20hospital%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20or%20the%20three%20murals%20they%20made%20for%20the%20Santori%20Resort%20at%20Mulshi%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20the%20studio%20keeps%20busy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20started%20my%20business%20in%20my%20fifties%2C%20much%20against%20everyone%E2%80%99s%20advice%20and%20with%20many%20negative%20comments%20from%20sceptics%20and%20naysayers.%20Some%20people%20felt%20I%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F215357%2Findia-philanthropy-david-rockefeller-shibulal-family-philanthropic-initiatives-changemakers-education%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etoo%20old%20to%20start%20a%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20something%20I%20was%20not%20experienced%20in.%20I%20am%20happy%20to%20say%20that%20I%20am%20still%20here%20and%20enjoying%20my%20work%20all%20while%20creating%20products%20that%20people%20truly%20appreciate%2C%E2%80%9D%20Naomi%20says%20with%20a%20smile.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FBook-shelf-1697535601.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20book%20shelf%20made%20with%20using%20a%20reclaimed%20piece%20of%20wood.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FBook-shelf-1697535601.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FBook-shelf-1697535601-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FBook-shelf-1697535601-500x667.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FBook-shelf-1697535601-768x1024.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FBook-shelf-1697535601-1152x1536.jpg%201152w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FBook-shelf-1697535601-640x853.jpg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FBook-shelf-1697535601-150x200.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332392%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20book%20shelf%20made%20with%20using%20a%20reclaimed%20piece%20of%20wood.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EAll%20picture%20credits%20to%20The%20Druid%E2%80%99s%20Garden.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697552503000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FNature-themed-wall-art_11zon-1697535460.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D332361%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Naomi%20and%20Yohann%20Pereira's%20venture%2C%20The%20Druid%E2%80%99s%20Garden%2C%20makes%20unique%2C%20aesthetic%20and%20sustainable%20products%20by%20using%20reclaimed%20and%20upcycled%20raw%20materials.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Aruna%20Raghuram%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332361%2Fmumbai-artist-mom-son-use-driftwood-and-mosaic-tiles-to-make-art-furniture%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Full%20Statement%20%7C%20Neville%20Roy%20Singham%20Rejects%20Allegations%20in%20the%20NewsClick%20Case%20as%20'Misleading'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F07105239%2F5mtb93eo_neville-roy-singham-1200_625x300_07_August_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EAmerican%20millionaire%20Neville%20Roy%20Singham%2C%20who%20has%20been%20named%20as%20an%20accused%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20terror%20case%2C%20has%20rejected%20the%20allegations%20that%20he%20is%20running%20a%20funding%20network%20affiliated%20to%20the%20Chinese%20government%E2%80%99s%20propaganda%20arm%20to%20spread%20China%E2%80%99s%20talking%20points%20around%20the%20world%2C%20including%20in%20India%20through%20media%20outlet%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20four-page%20rebuttal%2C%20available%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Singham%20called%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F08%2F05%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fneville-roy-singham-china-propaganda.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20article%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20first%20came%20out%20with%20allegations%20against%20him%20%E2%80%9Cmisleading%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20described%20the%20article%20as%20an%20%E2%80%9Cinnuendo-laden%20hit%20piece%E2%80%9D.%20Based%20on%20the%20August%205%20%3Cem%3ENYT%3C%2Fem%3E%20article%2C%20the%20Delhi%20Police%E2%80%99s%20special%20cell%20named%20him%20as%20an%20accused%20in%20the%20case%2C%20in%20which%20the%C2%A0editor%20and%20an%20employee%20of%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewere%20arrested%3Cem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EClose%20to%20100%20persons%2C%20including%20journalists%20and%20activists%2C%20were%20also%20raided.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECalling%20the%20%3Cem%3ENYT%3C%2Fem%3E%20piece%20%E2%80%9Ca%20great%20disservice%20to%20the%20cause%20of%20press%20freedom%E2%80%9D%2C%20Singham%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20%3Cem%3ENYT%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%20intentionally%20chose%20not%20to%20publish%20all%20the%20factual%20rebuttals%20that%20I%20provided%20to%20them%20on%20July%2022%2C%202023%2C%20prior%20to%20their%20publication%20date.%20The%C2%A0%3Cem%3ENYT%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20done%20a%20great%20disservice%20to%20the%20cause%20of%20press%20freedom.%20For%20this%20reason%2C%20I%20have%20decided%20to%20publicly%20address%20some%20of%20these%20points%20that%20I%20raised%2C%20and%20were%20ignored%20by%2C%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3ENYT%3C%2Fem%3E.%20I%20categorically%20deny%20and%20repudiate%20all%20claims%20of%20illegality%20and%20impropriety%20and%20wish%20to%20set%20the%20record%20straight%2C%E2%80%9D%20Singham%20said%20in%20his%20rebuttal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20allegations%20linking%20him%20to%20the%20Chinese%20government%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20do%20not%20work%20for%2C%20nor%20take%20instruction%20from%2C%20nor%20receive%20funding%20from%20the%20Propaganda%20Department%20or%20any%20division%20of%20the%20Chinese%20government%20or%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20China%2C%20as%20the%20FIR%20claims%20and%20is%20suggested%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3ENYT%3C%2Fem%3E%20article.%20In%20fact%2C%20I%20do%20not%20take%20orders%20from%20any%20government%20or%20political%20party%20in%20the%20world.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20denied%20the%20allegation%20that%20his%20open-source%20map%20project%20sought%20to%20undermine%20India%E2%80%99s%20territorial%20integrity.%20%E2%80%9CIn%202020%2C%20I%20was%20presented%20with%20an%20opportunity%20to%20sponsor%20a%20free%20and%20open-source%20software%20project%20that%20would%20allow%20anyone%20to%20create%20their%20own%20equal-area%20projection%20maps.%20While%20there%20are%20hundreds%20of%20ongoing%20international%20border%20disputes%2C%20including%20for%20example%2C%20between%20Canada%20and%20the%20United%20States%2C%20the%20goal%20was%20always%20to%20allow%20citizens%20of%20each%20country%20to%20produce%20maps%20that%20are%20consistent%20with%20their%20own%20laws%20and%20reflect%20their%20sovereign%20counties%E2%80%99%20national%20interests%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESingham%20said%20he%20chose%20to%20publicly%20address%20the%20allegations%20against%20him%2C%20as%20%3Cem%3ENYT%3C%2Fem%3E%20chose%20to%20%E2%80%9Cignore%E2%80%9D%20some%20of%20the%20points%20he%20had%20made.%20%E2%80%9CI%20categorically%20deny%20and%20repudiate%20all%20claims%20of%20illegality%20and%20impropriety%20and%20wish%20to%20set%20the%20record%20straight%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBelow%20is%20the%20full%20statement%20from%20Singham.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMy%20name%20is%20Neville%20Roy%20Singham.%20I%20founded%20and%20led%20ThoughtWorks%20Inc.%2C%20an%20IT%20company%2C%20for%2025%20years%20and%20sold%20it%20in%202017.%20I%20have%20been%20and%20remain%20solely%20a%20US%20citizen%20since%20birth.%20I%20currently%20reside%20in%20Shanghai%20(China).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20August%205%2C%202023%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F08%2F05%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fneville-roy-singham-china-propaganda.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3Ethe%C2%A0%3Ci%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0(NYT)%20ran%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0a%20misleading%20and%20innuendo-laden%20hit%20piece%20on%20me%20and%20others%20that%2C%20among%20other%20things%2C%20provoked%20a%20firestorm%20in%20India%20and%20inflamed%20the%20situation%20regarding%20the%20Indian%20news%20website%20portal%C2%A0%3Ci%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fi%3E.%20Twelve%20days%20after%20the%20publication%2C%20on%20August%2017%2C%20the%C2%A0Delhi%20Police%20Station%20Special%20Cell%20secretly%20prepared%20and%20issued%20a%20First%20Information%20Report%20(FIR).%20Full%20of%20defamatory%20allegations%20and%20factual%20errors%2C%20the%20FIR%20led%20to%20the%20interrogation%20of%20nearly%20100%20journalists%2C%20the%20detention%20of%20dozens%2C%20and%20the%20eventual%20arrest%20of%20two%20people%20on%20October%203%2C%202023.%20After%20the%20arrests%2C%20the%20FIR%20entered%20the%20public%20domain%2C%20the%20release%20of%20which%20is%20damaging%20to%20me%20and%20many%20others.%20The%20language%20used%20in%20the%20FIR%20strongly%20suggests%20that%20its%20claims%20were%20influenced%20by%20misinformation%20from%20the%C2%A0%3Ci%3ENYT%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0article.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20home%20to%20many%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20best%20journalists%20and%20writers.%20It%20has%20a%20vibrant%20press%20and%20media%20landscape.%20The%20news%20of%20the%20arrests%20and%20detentions%20deeply%20shocked%20and%20saddened%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20am%20disappointed%20that%20this%20is%20happening%20in%20India%2C%20a%20country%20close%20to%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20the%20ancestral%20home%20of%20my%20father%2C%20Archibald%20W.%20Singham%20(1932%E2%80%931991)%2C%20a%20participant%20in%20and%20historian%20of%20the%20Non-Aligned%20Movement.%20I%20write%20this%20as%20someone%20who%20dearly%20loves%20India%2C%20having%20had%20a%20long-standing%20relationship%20with%20the%20country%20and%20its%20people%2C%20from%20my%20first%20visit%20to%20Mumbai%20in%201964%2C%20at%20the%20age%20of%2011%2C%20to%20the%20years%20I%20spent%20in%20the%20Indian%20software%20industry.%20Beginning%20in%20the%20early%202000s%2C%20I%20spent%20considerable%20time%20in%20India%2C%20opening%20ThoughtWorks%20offices%20across%20India%2C%20including%20in%20Bangalore%2C%20Pune%2C%20Chennai%2C%20Coimbatore%2C%20Delhi%2C%20and%20Hyderabad.%20Along%20with%20many%20brilliant%20Indian%20colleagues%2C%20I%20helped%20establish%20many%20conferences%20and%20projects%20that%20advanced%20the%20Indian%20software%20industry.%20I%20remain%20proud%20that%20we%20collectively%20built%20world-class%2C%20advanced%2C%20Agile%20software%20development%20centers%20in%20India%20%E2%80%93%20the%20first%20in%20the%20Global%20South.%20We%20successfully%20highlight%20the%20talents%20of%20India%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%C2%A0%3Ci%3ENYT%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3Eintentionally%20chose%20not%20to%20publish%20all%20the%20factual%20rebuttals%20that%20I%20provided%20to%20them%20on%20July%2022%2C%202023%2C%20prior%20to%20their%20publication%20date.%20The%C2%A0%3Ci%3ENYT%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0has%20done%20a%20great%20disservice%20to%20the%20cause%20to%20press%20freedom.%20For%20this%20reason%2C%20I%20have%20decided%20to%20publicly%20address%20some%20of%20these%20points%20that%20I%20raised%20to%2C%20and%20were%20ignored%20by%2C%20the%C2%A0%3Ci%3ENYT%3C%2Fi%3E.%20I%20categorically%20deny%20and%20repudiate%20all%20claims%20of%20illegality%20and%20impropriety%20and%20wish%20to%20set%20the%20record%20straight.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20regarding%20the%20provenance%20of%20the%20funds%20invested%20in%20NewsClick.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20urge%20all%20those%20following%20these%20events%20to%20read%20the%20full%20statement%20by%20Jason%20Pfetcher%2C%20manager%20of%20Worldwide%20Media%20Holdings%20LLC%2C%20the%20US-based%20organization%20that%20made%20an%20investment%20in%C2%A0%3Ci%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fi%3E.%20The%20article%20published%20in%C2%A0%3Ci%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0can%20be%20found%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fstatement-on-worldwide-media-holdings-investment-in-newsclick%2Farticle67390484.ece%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20covers%20the%20details%20of%20the%20investment%20in%C2%A0%3Ci%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0and%20categorically%20repudiates%20the%20false%20allegations%20surrounding%20the%20source%20of%20the%20funds%20that%20were%20sent%20to%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20on%20the%20provenance%20of%20my%20funds%20and%20a%20rejection%20of%20the%20false%20claims%20that%20I%20have%20received%20funds%20from%20any%20government%20or%20political%20party%2C%20including%20China%20and%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20ThoughtWorks%20was%20sold%20to%20Apax%20Partners%2C%20a%20global%20private%20equity%20firm.%20As%20the%20majority%20shareholder%2C%20I%20received%20substantial%20proceeds%20from%20this%20sale.%20I%20donated%20a%20significant%20share%20of%20this%20to%20US%20charities.%20I%20am%20keenly%20aware%20of%20my%20extreme%20financial%20privilege%20and%20for%20this%20reason%20I%20decided%20to%20donate%20much%20of%20my%20personal%20wealth%20to%20non-profits%20and%20causes%20that%20advance%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20poor.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20do%20not%20have%20other%20sources%20of%20funds%20besides%20my%20personal%20savings%2C%20revenue%20from%20the%20sale%20of%20the%20company%2C%20and%20the%20subsequent%20income%20from%20my%20personal%20investments.%20Other%20than%20ThoughtWorks%20%E2%80%93%20which%20had%20some%20government%20clients%20over%20the%20years%2C%20including%20the%20US%2C%20UK%2C%20and%20Australian%20governments%20(but%C2%A0%3Ci%3Enot%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0including%20China)%20%E2%80%93%20I%20have%20never%20received%20funding%20from%20any%20government%20or%20political%20party.%20I%20file%20a%20comprehensive%20tax%20return%20in%20the%20US%20every%20year%20and%20have%20always%20hired%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20top%20accounting%20and%20tax%20firms%20to%20carefully%20review%20all%20aspects%20of%20my%20financial%20affairs.%20The%20provenance%20of%20all%20my%20money%20is%20without%20doubt.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20was%20shocked%20to%20see%20the%20absurd%20attempt%20to%20connect%20me%20to%20the%20Chinese%20telecom%20companies%2C%20Xiaomi%20and%20Vivo%2C%20in%20the%20FIR.%20I%20have%20no%20knowledge%20of%20their%20activities%20in%20India.%20I%20have%20never%20had%20contact%20with%2C%20directly%20or%20indirectly%20received%20funding%20from%2C%20nor%20worked%20on%20behalf%20of%20these%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThird%2C%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20me%20working%20for%20or%20taking%20instructions%20from%20any%20government%20or%20political%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20let%20me%20be%20very%20clear.%20I%20do%20not%20work%20for%2C%20nor%20take%20instruction%20from%2C%20nor%20receive%20funding%20from%20the%20Propaganda%20Department%20or%20any%20division%20of%20the%20Chinese%20government%20or%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20China%2C%20as%20the%20FIR%20claims%20and%20is%20suggested%20in%20the%20NYT%20article.%20In%20fact%2C%20I%20do%20not%20take%20orders%20from%20any%20government%20or%20political%20party%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20am%20not%20now%20and%20have%20never%20been%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20China.%20In%20fact%2C%20Chinese%20citizens%20are%20the%20only%20people%20eligible%20for%20membership%2C%20a%20requirement%20of%20the%20constitution%20adopted%20by%20the%208th%20National%20Congress%20of%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20China%20in%201956.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20have%20spent%20considerable%20periods%20of%20my%20life%20in%20several%20countries%2C%20including%20Jamaica%2C%20the%20United%20States%2C%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20India%2C%20China%2C%20Brazil%2C%20and%20South%20Africa.%20I%20have%20visited%20over%2060%20countries.%20I%20have%20had%20the%20great%20privilege%20of%20meeting%20and%20knowing%20working-class%20leaders%20and%20people%20in%20many%20of%20these%20countries.%20I%20also%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20meet%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20intellectuals%2C%20journalists%2C%20and%20leaders%20of%20all%20types%2C%20including%20public%20health%20officials%2C%20university%20leaders%2C%20government%20functionaries%20and%20leaders%2C%20political%20leaders%2C%20and%20CEOs.%20Nothing%20from%20my%20diverse%20life%20experience%20suggests%20I%20am%20controlled%20by%20others.%20Rather%20this%20experience%20has%20reinforced%20my%20commitment%20to%20and%20care%20for%20all%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20peoples%20and%20to%20improve%20cross-country%20solidarity%20and%20collaboration.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFourth%2C%20on%20the%20accusation%20that%20I%20have%20broken%20any%20laws%20and%20my%20vigilance%20towards%20legal%20compliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20reject%20the%20allegation%20of%20fraudulent%20infusion%20of%20funds%20through%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccomplex%20web%20of%20several%20entities%E2%80%9D%20as%20mentioned%20in%20the%20FIR%20and%20in%20the%20NYT%20article.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20also%20reject%20any%20innuendo%20that%20I%20violate%20any%20Indian%20or%20US%20law%20by%20working%20with%20banned%20organizations.%20There%20is%20just%20no%20proof%20of%20such%20accusations%20because%20they%20are%20untrue.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHaving%20run%20a%20multinational%20company%20(ThoughtWorks)%20for%20many%20years%2C%20I%20learned%20the%20vital%20importance%20of%20carefully%20following%20the%20laws%20of%20all%20the%20countries%20in%20which%20we%20conducted%20business.%20My%20record%20as%20chairman%20speaks%20for%20itself%20in%20this%20period.%20International%20philanthropy%20is%20a%20complex%20area%20involving%20deep%20knowledge%20of%20many%20laws%20and%20tax%20systems%20in%20the%20US%20and%20abroad.%20It%20requires%20expert%20advice%20and%20donor%20structures%20developed%20by%20top%20legal%2C%20tax%2C%20and%20accounting%20firms.%20I%20have%20acquired%20and%20followed%20such%20advice%20throughout%20my%20philanthropic%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20consequence%20of%20this%20strict%20adherence%20to%20laws%20requires%20more%20than%20one%20legal%20entity%20and%20many%20detailed%20compliance%20structures.%20For%20example%2C%20there%20are%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20different%20types%20of%20non-profit%20organizations%20in%20the%20US%2C%20and%20each%20must%20be%20set%20up%20with%20independent%20boards.%20Additionally%2C%20I%20have%20learned%20that%20good%20internal%20compliance%20measures%20should%20be%20established%20and%20to%20always%20seek%20outside%20professional%20services%20firms%20for%20advice%2C%20compliance%20assistance%2C%20and%20filing%20of%20tax%20and%20other%20reports.%20US%20entities%20and%20citizens%20must%20vigorously%20follow%20many%20regulations%2C%20including%20those%20of%20the%20US%20Office%20of%20Foreign%20Assets%20Control.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMy%20goal%20was%20to%20successfully%20donate%20money.%20Being%20careless%20or%20not%20strictly%20adhering%20to%20the%20laws%20around%20legally%20proscribed%20banned%20organizations%20would%20destroy%20all%20the%20objectives%20of%20making%20donations%20and%20endanger%20all%20recipients%20of%20philanthropic%20donations.%3Cb%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFifth%2C%20on%20my%20beliefs%20and%20attitudes%20towards%20giving%20away%20my%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20probity%20and%20transparency%20of%20my%20political%20beliefs%20span%20many%20decades%2C%20beginning%20with%20my%20teenage%20years.%20Like%20many%20in%20my%20generation%2C%20I%20could%20not%20accept%20the%20discrepancy%20between%20the%20wealth%20of%20a%20few%20versus%20the%20misery%20of%20millions.%20In%20those%20formative%20years%2C%20I%20began%20to%20believe%20that%20everyone%2C%20including%20those%20born%20with%20any%20type%20of%20privilege%2C%20should%20try%20to%20spend%20at%20least%20part%20of%20their%20life%20building%20a%20world%20based%20on%20the%20dignity%20of%20the%20common%20people.%20I%20decided%20that%20at%20my%20age%20and%20with%20my%20extreme%20privilege%2C%20the%20best%20thing%20I%20could%20do%20was%20to%20give%20away%20most%20of%20my%20money%20in%20my%20lifetime.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELike%20most%20philanthropists%20with%20a%20high%20net%20worth%2C%20I%20chose%20to%20give%20money%20to%20organizations%20and%20causes%20whose%20work%20I%20generally%20like%2C%20respect%2C%20and%20admire.%20These%20organizations%20have%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20donated%20money%20to%2C%20or%20invested%20funds%20in%2C%20various%20US%20and%20foreign%20nonprofits.%20US%20nonprofits%20file%20publicly%20available%20990s%2C%20including%20disclosing%20their%20investments%20and%20grantmaking%20activities.%20These%20nonprofits%20are%20controlled%20by%20their%20respective%20boards%20and%20officers.%20Although%20I%20have%20been%20known%20to%20share%20my%20personal%20views%20with%20many%20people%2C%20including%20people%20involved%20in%20the%20organizations%2C%20I%20do%20not%20control%20these%20organizations%20and%20have%20respected%20and%20upheld%20the%20integrity%20of%20those%20that%20receive%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20believe%20that%20the%20wealth%20of%20society%20is%20created%20collectively.%20Given%20the%20large%20amount%20of%20money%20I%20made%20from%20the%20sale%2C%20my%20personal%20attitude%20is%20and%20was%20that%20I%20should%20consider%20myself%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctrustee%E2%80%9D%20of%20this%20money.%20My%20task%20would%20be%20to%20try%20to%20ensure%20it%20benefits%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20poor%20and%20working%20peoples%20of%20the%20world%2C%20and%20not%20seek%20publicity%20for%20doing%20so.%3Cb%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESixth%2C%20on%20the%20innuendos%20regarding%20my%20continued%20professional%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20core%20element%20of%20my%20philanthropic%20goal%20is%20to%20assist%20projects%20dedicated%20to%20systematically%20and%20permanently%20eliminating%20world%20poverty%2C%20in%20which%20hunger%20plays%20an%20essential%20part.%20While%20working%20with%20farmer%20cooperatives%2C%20it%20became%20clear%20that%2C%20despite%20being%20the%20core%20producers%20of%20food%20that%20nourishes%20the%20world%2C%20many%20farmers%2C%20and%20their%20families%20in%20large%20parts%20of%20the%20Global%20South%20are%20often%20among%20the%20hungriest.%20A%20key%20question%20is%20how%20to%20change%20the%20portion%20of%20the%20total%20world%20food%20chain%20that%20can%20be%20equitably%20redirected%20to%20the%20original%20producers.%20This%20needs%20a%20comprehensive%20approach%20that%20addresses%20the%20social%2C%20economic%2C%20and%20cultural%20aspects%20of%20rural%20life%20and%20is%20not%20a%20pretext%20for%20eliminating%20rural%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChina%20is%20a%20large%20country%20paying%20attention%20to%20eliminating%20absolute%20poverty%20and%20cultivating%20rural%20revitalization.%20It%20is%20also%20a%20large%20importer%20of%20food%20products.%20Because%20of%20my%20accumulated%20business%20knowledge%2C%20I%20dedicated%20my%20time%20here%20to%20assisting%20Global%20South%20cooperatives%2C%20especially%20in%20Africa%20and%20Latin%20America%2C%20in%20achieving%20better%20and%20fairer%20prices%2C%20advancing%20the%20technical%20capacities%20of%20cooperatives%2C%20and%20encouraging%20scientific%20and%20agricultural%20exchanges.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20am%20under%20no%20illusion%20that%20there%20is%20a%20singular%20path%20to%20development%20for%20the%20Global%20South.%20I%20believe%20that%20all%20countries%20in%20the%20Global%20South%20can%20learn%20from%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESeventh%2C%20on%20the%20claim%20that%20an%20open-source%20map%20project%20sought%20to%20undermine%20India%E2%80%99s%20territorial%20integrity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20I%20was%20presented%20with%20an%20opportunity%20to%20sponsor%20a%20free%20and%20open-source%20software%20project%20that%20would%20allow%20anyone%20to%20create%20their%20own%20equal-area%20projection%20maps.%20While%20there%20are%20hundreds%20of%20ongoing%20international%20border%20disputes%2C%20including%20for%20example%2C%20between%20Canada%20and%20the%20United%20States%2C%20the%20goal%20was%20always%20to%20allow%20citizens%20of%20each%20country%20to%20produce%20maps%20that%20are%20consistent%20with%20their%20own%20laws%20and