0A%20Banker%20Has%20Been%20Photographing%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20Flamingos%20For%207%20Years%20in%20a%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EVidyasagar%20Hariharan%20found%20his%20purpose%20in%20life%20thanks%20to%20running.%20In%202016%2C%20the%20Mumbai%20resident%20joined%20a%20marathon%20coaching%20club.%20While%20going%20for%20a%20run%2C%20his%20marathon%20mates%20spoke%20about%20going%20cycling%20to%20Sewri%2C%20to%20see%20flamingos.%20The%20banker%20was%20pleasantly%20surprised%20when%20he%20learnt%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F128588%2Fmumbai-thane-flamingo-sanctuary-maharashtra-mangrove-cell%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eflamingos%3C%2Fa%3E%20come%20to%20Mumbai%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20curiosity%20piqued%2C%20the%20bird%20lover%20cycled%20with%20his%20friends%20to%20Sewri%20the%20next%20morning.%20What%20he%20saw%20bowled%20him%20over.%20He%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20the%20wading%20birds%20the%20first%20time%20he%20laid%20eyes%20on%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20his%20marathon%20coach%20about%20his%20experience%20and%20was%20informed%20by%20him%20that%20there%20was%20a%20small%20lake%20behind%20the%20NRI%20complex%20residential%20area%20in%20Navi%20Mumbai%2C%20to%20which%20flamingos%20throng%20in%20thousands%20during%20the%20season%20and%20could%20be%20seen%20in%20much%20closer%20quarters%20than%20Sewri.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVidyasagar%20can%20perfectly%20recall%20that%20Saturday%20morning%20in%20March%202016%20like%20it%20was%20yesterday.%20He%20calls%20what%20he%20saw%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331893%2Fmental-health-care-therapy-counselling-affordable-startups-india-online%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98magic%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20heard%20a%20loud%20noise%20as%20we%20were%20nearing%20the%20waterbody.%20It%20was%20the%20sound%20of%20thousands%20of%20flamingos%20cackling.%20The%20rising%20sun%20painted%20the%20murky%20tidal%20waters%20and%20the%20pink%20birds%20golden.%20I%20was%20enamoured%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2047-year-old.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCsodrLsyPCz%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCsodrLsyPCz%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCsodrLsyPCz%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20%F0%9D%9A%85%F0%9D%9A%92%F0%9D%9A%8D%F0%9D%9A%A2%F0%9D%9A%8A%F0%9D%9A%9C%F0%9D%9A%8A%F0%9D%9A%90%F0%9D%9A%8A%F0%9D%9A%9B%20%F0%9D%99%B7%F0%9D%9A%8A%F0%9D%9A%9B%F0%9D%9A%92%F0%9D%9A%91%F0%9D%9A%8A%F0%9D%9A%9B%F0%9D%9A%8A%F0%9D%9A%97%20(%40flamingosofmumbai)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3EHaving%20an%20interest%20in%20photography%20and%20birds%2C%20Vidyasagar%20then%20invested%20in%20a%20good%20camera%20and%20began%20visiting%20the%20wetlands%20every%20week.%20He%20also%20started%20extensive%20research%20on%20the%20birds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20says%20that%20flamingos%20began%20visiting%20Mumbai%20in%20the%201990s.%20A%20Bombay%20Natural%20History%20Society%20(BNHS)%20study%20found%201.2%20lakh%20Greater%20and%20Lesser%20flamingos%20(two%20species)%20in%20Mumbai%20%E2%80%94%20mainly%20the%20Thane%20creek%20%E2%80%94%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThane%20creek%2C%20which%20separates%20Mumbai%20island%20from%20the%20mainland%20is%20the%20key%20to%20this%20ecosystem%20and%20here%20is%20where%20the%20flamingos%20arrive%20from%20Kutch%20and%20some%20probably%20(the%20greater%20flamingos)%20all%20the%20way%20from%20the%20Persian%20gulf.%20Mumbai%20has%20such%20a%20beautiful%20mangrove%20and%20wetland%20habitat%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Vidyasagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVisiting%20the%20numerous%20wetlands%20in%20the%20city%20and%20documenting%20the%20beautiful%20birds%20led%20to%20a%20deeper%20understanding%20about%20the%20issues%20around%20wetlands%20and%20the%20natural%20history%20phenomenon.%20He%20decided%20to%20create%20awareness%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20conserving%20the%20urban%20wetlands%20through%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fflamingosofmumbai%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInstagram%20page.%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHere%20are%2010%20pictures%20that%20show%20how%20important%20it%20is%20to%20preserve%20the%20mangroves%20and%20wetlands%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Col%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20lake%20behind%20the%20NRI%20complex%2C%20Navi%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Fol%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201066px)%20100vw%2C%201066px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPicture-1-1697205202.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221066%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20lake%20behind%20the%20NRI%20complex%2C%20Navi%2